newsitem.title: USA: Iowa-S Minn cattle not fully established - USDA.
newsitem.headline: Iowa-S Minn cattle not fully established - USDA.

text.p: Steers and heifers were not fully established with few sales steady, compared with Wednesday's close, USDA said.
Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1200-1300 lbs few 70.00-71.50.
Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1100-1200 lbs few 70.00-71.50.
On a carcass basis, steers and heifers were steady on few early sales.
Steers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1200-1300 lbs 112.00-113.00 few 114.00.
Heifers - Select to mostly Choice 2-4 1050-1200 lbs 112.00-113.00. Reported sales for Wed - 600 Week to Date - 18,700
